Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Calculation of the amplitude associated to Goldstone diagrams with alphabetic \
indices\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.888315861110175*^9, 3.8883159051561947`*^9}, {
  3.8883159887111607`*^9, 3.888316043821027*^9}, {3.888316084808132*^9, 
  3.888316094409692*^9}, {3.9080017355726566`*^9, 3.9080017402516623`*^9}, {
  3.9082509561005807`*^9, 
  3.9082509656258793`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a2786b7c-01a1-4e0f-a727-\
b79fb4edf1a8"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The two time integrals are evaluated in two steps. First, one computes the \
integral over ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["t", "1"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "87eebfec-47b9-43c0-bd2e-1090d6b3b3ce"],
 " (dummy time), by solving a linear system with a parameter (the second \
frequency). At first order, the frequency variable which is evaluated after \
integration by ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["t", "1"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e5f47f69-5cad-424b-9df2-fe355abc0bbb"],
 " is labeled as \[Epsilon]. Consequently, the time difference multiplying \
\[Epsilon] must contain the time ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["t", 
    RowBox[{"1", " "}]], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8369edd3-ce73-4536-9bc0-5422e879e6df"],
 ", otherwise the integration fails.  Next, the integration over (t-t\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]) is performed, solving a single linear equation, obtained \
by equating the coefficient of (t-t\[CloseCurlyQuote]) in the total \
polynomial to zero. Note that the time interval that multiplies \[Digamma]  \
must contain either t or t\[CloseCurlyQuote]. Consequently, in the \
denominators of the energy representation, two \[OpenCurlyQuote]omegas\
\[CloseCurlyQuote] may appear, depending on the topology of the unoriented \
Goldstone diagram. Besides, the time interval multiplying \[Digamma]  shall \
never coincide with the one associated with \[Epsilon], otherwise the \
implemented time sequence is ill-defined."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8883163242658205`*^9, 3.8883163554476023`*^9}, {
   3.8883164071679173`*^9, 3.8883165187772655`*^9}, {3.888316549145891*^9, 
   3.888316725014002*^9}, {3.889589439475727*^9, 3.8895894549299793`*^9}, {
   3.889590402006256*^9, 3.8895904024655275`*^9}, {3.892181261167833*^9, 
   3.8921812646587067`*^9}, 3.9080021721087875`*^9, {3.9398819758263073`*^9, 
   3.9398820022169285`*^9}, {3.9399956753348913`*^9, 3.939995779248702*^9}, {
   3.9399958126995935`*^9, 3.939995873059267*^9}, 
   3.945419695509862*^9},ExpressionUUID->"97e48545-8fb4-4799-bace-\
23db46069f4d"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"GGFTotalPolynomial", " ", "=", " ", 
